<div class="col-sm-12 no-padding botMARG">
    <h1 class="contentPageH1">EMOTIONAL FIRST AID<small class="contentH1-small">&nbsp;CERTIFICATE</small></h1>
    <ol class="breadcrumb">
        <li class="contentp">@Html.ActionLink("Home", "Index", "Home")</li>
        <li class="contentp">@Html.ActionLink("All Certificates", "AllCertificates", "Certificates")</li>
        <li class="active contentp">Emotional First Aid</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<div class="col-sm-8 mid-padding">

    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-body">


            <h1 class="contentH1">Description</h1><hr class="hrp" />
            <p class="contentp">
                The objective of the Emotional First Aid is to enhance the knowledge revolving around emotions and

                mental health. This workshop will cover areas such as:
            </p>
            <ul class="contentp">
                <li>Exploring the emotional being of a person</li>

                <li>
                    What are contributing factors affecting one’s emotion, we will explore areas such as:
                    <ul>
                        <li>mental health</li>

                        <li>
                            domestic related
                        </li>

                        <li>psychosocial (finances, relationships, employment, etc.)</li>

                        <li>alcohol and drug use</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>

                <li>How to assess one’s emotions and mental status</li>

                <li>Treatment options (mindfulness, medication, psychotherapy and others)</li>

                <li>Preventative strategies</li>
            </ul>
            <br />

            <h1 class="contentH1">Workshop Prerequisite</h1><hr class="hrp" />

            <ul class="contentp">
                <li>
                    Frontline workers, nurses, social workers, community support workers, child and youth workers, crisis workers, students and others working in the community
                </li>

                <li>A printed certificate will be printed for all those attended</li>
            </ul>
            <br />

            <h1 class="contentH1">Course Duration and Schedule</h1><hr class="hrp" />
            <ul class="contentp">
                <li>TBD</li>

                <li>9:00am to 4:00pm</li>
            </ul><br />
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h1 class="contentH1">Fees</h1><hr class="hrp" />
                    <ul class="contentp">
                        <li>$30.00 CAD (This workshop has been subsidized, original price $215.00 CAD; savings of $185.00 CAD)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

        


            <p class="contentp">
                This program does not require approval under the Private Career Colleges Act, 2005.

            </p>
        </div>
    </div>


    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block contentH2"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-send"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;@Html.ActionLink("GO TO CERTIFICATES DIRECTORY", "AllCertificates", "Certificates")</button>
    <br />
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-lg btn-block contentH2"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-map-marker"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;@Html.ActionLink("GO TO CAMPUS DIRECTORY", "Index", "Campuses")</button>

    <br />
</div>

